quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,"Xurmo weynee oo huf Magaca Rabbigaa, aad u Sarreeya"
  87,2,"Kan abuuray (uunka), ee hagaajiyey"
  87,3,"Oo ah Kan wax kasta qaddaray, markaa ku hagay (qaddarkiisa)"
  87,4,Oo ah Kan soo saara daaqa
  87,5,Oo misna ka dhiga xaabo madow
  87,6,Waxaan kaa yeeli doonnaa inaad akhrido (Qur’aanka) mana illaawi doontid
  87,7,"Wuxuu Allaah doono ma’ahee, Wuxuu Og yahay waxa muuqda iyo waxa qarsoonba"
  87,8,Oo Waxaanu kuu fududeyn midda sahlan (Islaamka)
  87,9,"Ee waani, markay waanadu wax tari"
  87,10,Kan isagu baqa baa ku waano qaadan
  87,11,Oo kan khayr laawaha ah baa ka fogaan (waanada)
  87,12,Kaasoo geli doona Naar aad u weyn
  87,13,"Markaa dhexdeeda kuma noolaan doono, mana ku dhiman doono"
  87,14,Waxaa dhab ahaan liibaani qofka daahiriya naftiisa
  87,15,Oo xurmo weyneeya Magaca Rabbigi oo salaadda tukada
  87,16,Balse waxaad door biddaan nolosha adduunkan
  87,17,Aakhirada baase khayr badan oo daa’insan
  87,18,Hubaal (hadal)kani wuxuu ku yaal Kututbtii hore
  87,19,Kutubtii Ibraahiim iyo Muuse
  88,1,Mawuusan kuu iman warka dabooshada
  88,2,Wejiyo (qaar) maalintaas waxay ahaan kuwo dulleysan
  88,3,"Howlan, aad u daallan"
  88,4,Waxay Geli Naar aad u kulul
  88,5,Waxaa laga waraabin il kulul oo kareysa
  88,6,Ma laha wax cunto ah qodxo maahee
  88,7,"Kaasoo aan wax cayilin, gaajona wax ka tarin"
  88,8,"Wejiyo (kale) Maalintaas, waxay ahaan kuwo nicmeysan"
  88,9,Raalli ah dadaalkoodii darti
  88,10,Ku jira Beer sare gudaheed
  88,11,Aysan ku maqleyn hadal macno darro ah
  88,12,Dhexdeeda waxaa ah il socota
  88,13,Dhexdeeda waxaa ah sariirro la kor yeelay
  88,14,Iyo koobab diyaar laga dhigay
  88,15,Iyo barkimooyin la safay
  88,16,Iyo gogollo la fidshey
  88,17,"Mawaysan haddaba eegin geela, sida loo abuuray"
  88,18,"Iyo cirka, sida loo kor yeelay"
  88,19,"Iyo buuraha, sida loo dhidbay"
  88,20,"Iyo dhulka, sida loo fidiyey"
  88,21,"Ee wax waani, waayo waxaad adigu uun tahay waaniye"
  88,22,Ma tihid mid qasab ku leh ee ilaaliya
  88,23,Kii kastoo se dhabarka jeediya oo gaalooba
  88,24,Wuxuu Allaah ku cadaabi cadaab aad u weyn
  88,25,Xaqiiq waa Xaggayaga meel noqodkoodu
  88,26,Markaas hubaal Annaga bay na saaran tahay xisaabintooda
  89,1,Waxaan ku dhaartay waaberiga
  89,2,Iyo habeennada tobanka ah
  89,3,Iyo dhabanka iyo witirka(tirada is dheer)
  89,4,Iyo habeenka marka uu tago
  89,5,Runtii taasi waxaa ugu sugan dhaar kuwaa garashada leh
  89,6,Mawaadan u fiirsan sida Rabbigaa u galay (reer) Caad
  89,7,"Qolodii Iram, ee lahaa saraha aad u dhaadheer"
  89,8,Aan wax la mid ah laga sameyn magaalooyinka kale
  89,9,"Iyo (sida uu u galay) Thamuud, ee kala dhambalayey dhadhaabyo waaweyn tog gudahi ah (ay ka dhigtaan guryo iy jidad)"
  89,10,"Iyo (sida uu u galay) Fircoon, ee lahaa ciidammada tirada badan"
  89,11,Kuwaasoo ku qooqay magaalooyinka
  89,12,Oo ku badiyey fasahaad dhexdeeda
  89,13,Markaasuu Rabbigaa ku shubay korkooda noocyo kala duwan oo cadaab daran ah
  89,14,Hubaal Rabbigaa baa u jeeda oo arkaya
  89,15,"Ee ma aadmiga, marka uu Rabbigi imtixaano, oo sharfo oo u nicmeeyo wuxuu yidhaahdaa: Rabbigay waa i sharfay"
  89,16,"Markase uu (si kale) u imtixaano oo ku ciriirsho risiqa, wuxuu yidhaahdaa; Rabbigay waa i liiday"
  89,17,Mayee’ bal ma daryeeshaan agoonka
  89,18,Oo iskuma boorrisaan quudinta miskiinka
  89,19,Oo waxaad ku cuntaan xaqdarro dhaxalka idinkoo booli ku cunaya (wax kasta) si aan kala saar lahayn
  89,20,Oo waxaad jeceshihiin Maalka jaceyl aad u daran
  89,21,Mayee! Marka dhulka laga dhigo budo
  89,22,Oo Rabbigaa yimaado iyo (sidoo kale) malaa’igta oo saf saf ah
  89,23,"Oo laga yeelo Naarta mid muuqata Maalintaas. Maalintaas buu Aadmigu waansami, maxayse waantoobidda (markaa) u tari"
  89,24,"Wuxuu odhan: Alla haddaan wax horay ugu soo dirsan lahaa noloshaydatan"
  89,25,Maalintaas se cidna wax uguma cadaabto (wuxuun la mid ah) Cadaabkiisa
  89,26,"Oo cidi wax uma xirxirto, (wuxun la mid ah) Xirxiriddiisa"
  89,27,Naf yahay adiga xasillooneey
  89,28,"U noqo Rabbigaa, _adigoo raalli ka ah oo raalli lagaa yahay"
  89,29,Ee gal addoomaheyga dhexdood
  89,30,Oo gal Jannadeyda